{
  "stem": "2533.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then there were other things we cooked.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The farmers used to come along, and we had money so we were able to buy and all that, but we didn't starve.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'40.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was a hard winter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was very, very hard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I can't remember because we still were able to bake bread-- bread, and that was the most important thing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then to get some-- some flour or we used to go to the mill and get something from them because we had a lot of farmers who were friend of ours.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And maybe a bit of grain and all that, so we-- once we had flour and maybe beans and then other things and-- and all that, so it wasn't too bad, you know.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We could go out to-- to-- we had money to buy, still, milk or cheese and all that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was not easy, but we just managed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But then the 18th of May, that was '41, we went to work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when we came back, we were told not to go home anymore.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My mother, my grandmother, my great grandmother, and neighbor, Mrs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Kalb, ?] they were hidden at our place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had a double wall in the-- in the barn where-- where the horse and the cow was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So it was a double wall, and it was made up so that it didn't look like a double wall.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they were hiding there because they were too old to go to work or not feeling well, [? anyhow ?] grandmother and parents.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And all the elderly people and all the children who were at homes, at homes, they were taken away, and never saw them anymore.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
